      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/11/47",
      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَنْ شِرَاءِ مَمْلُوكِ أَهْلِ اَلذِّمَّةِ فَقَالَ \"إِذَا أَقَرُّوا لَهُمْ بِذَلِكَ فَاشْتَرِ وَ اِنْكِحْ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3818 - Aban narrated from Ismail ibn Al-Fadl, who said: \"I asked Abu Abdullah (as) about purchasing a slave from the People of the Book (Ahl al-Dhimma).\"\nImam (as) replied: \"If they acknowledge ownership of the slave, then buy and marry.\""
        ]
      }
    },
